values:
It has been a while:

on 4.2.04 I did Relay for Life and must have walked at least 15 miles

Other than that, not much to report.
I walked 6 miles today -- my longest walk yet!
Happy Birthday to our team captain! Have a wonderful day Kate!

Yay! I finally remembered to make an entry! Today I walked 3 miles. Tomorrow I'm planning to go 5 or 6. 

A little question for everybody (just to get some discussion going): How fast is everyone walking? I'm going about 3 mph, and I'm hoping thats about normal. I don't want to show up at the walk and be left in everyone's dust!

Have a good day!

I walked a little over 2 miles today (3.21.04)

My knees are killing me!
